    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly, while I love whole wheat flour and use it frequently, I encourage you to try whole wheat spelt flour. Maybe it is just a mind trick, but I swear the spelt tastes nuttier and fresher&#8230;not sure why since the oils in whole wheat are probably less likely to go rancid since it is more popular than spelt. At any rate, I&#39;ve gone to spelt and won&#39;t go back to whole wheat, even though spelt costs me an arm and a leg.<br />I can hardly wait to try these cookies (with spelt!). I swear I eat cacao nibs by the handful&#8230;sans anything.</p>
    </div>

