  <li id="comment-20672" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2010/12/wade-way-in/#comment-20672"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-01-09T18:23:33-05:00">Sunday, January 9, 2011 at 6:23 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi Molly!<br />Melanie asked about raw vs. roasted cacao nibs. My health food store only had raw. At their direction, I roasted them on a dry cookie sheet in a 250-degree oven for about 15 minutes shaking them every so often. It made my house smell like the Godiva store and they&#39;re perfect in these cookies! <br />Michele</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
